'''The Bonny Bounty''' was a drinking establishment located on the moon of [[Bogg 4]]. It was known as a haven for [[Mercenary/Legends|mercenaries]] and [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunters]]. The inside of the dimly lit cantina was furnished with long tables, guttering candles and a large fireplace. In [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]], the young orphan [[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett]] met a thief named [[Aia]] just outside the Bonny Bounty. A [[Diollan]] and a [[Rodian/Legends|Rodian]] patron remarked that pickpockets such as Aia were not welcome inside the cantina, but in truth the atmosphere of the Bounty catered to a wide variety of clientele.

